title: I didnt get the 10 years old gift! Please help me
body: I didnt get the 10 years old celebration gift!

replies.body: Rest easy, gifts are still being sent out.  Stay up to date on our [support banner](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/227317608--Sept-14-Anniversary-gifts-are-currently-being-distributed-You-may-not-receive-them-right-away-so-please-be-patient-) as we've just extended the gifting period to the 30th.  Hang tight, they will be coming!
